description: The Sky machine protocol is a project invested by the Swiss consortium Crypto Valley Venture Capital in 2017. It is the design of bionic intelligent robots and the development of professional chips. The project takes three years. In the first year, the company established a certificate system, established a community, and promoted and sold products (mineral machines and electronic products) for cooperation and contracted projects. In the second year, the company began to use the products sold to simulate the matching of human-machines. According to the training results, the research and development of the chip; in the third year, the bionic products are launched into the market, and the blockchain plays a management role in the product, and all products will become the nodes of artificial intelligence.
name: THESMP
